{"tid":502750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Lonely Lonely Christmas","createTime":"2017-12-18T08:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T08:22:54.000Z","uid":131064,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bad3a550c47993901a059520e1c069d885bba487","tid":502750,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T08:22:54.000Z","msg":"【警棍襲途人罪成】朱經緯還押　獄中過聖誕　12月29日判刑<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>真係好好既生日禮物</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/chu-14_v6Lqg_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fchu-14_v6Lqg_1200x0.png&h=58b6902f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n退休警司朱經緯在2014年佔領運動期間，涉嫌以警棍襲擊途人，距今1118日，朱被控一項襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，今日（18日）下午在東區裁判法院被判罪名成立。主任裁判官錢禮決定，朱經緯需還押，待12月29日（周五）判刑，換言之，於12月25日58歲生日的朱經緯，需於獄中過聖誕及生日。<br />\n<br />\n辯方律師指，朱經緯加入警隊35年，服務社會，請裁判官考慮判處社會服務令。辯方又指，朱經緯於12月25日生日，希望可申請保釋等候判刑。惟裁判官指朱經緯所干犯的為嚴重罪行，須還押等候判刑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E6%A3%8D%E8%A5%B2%E9%80%94%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E6%9C%B1%E7%B6%93%E7%B7%AF%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC-%E7%8D%84%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%8E%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95-12%E6%9C%8829%E6%97%A5%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91/#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25A3%258D%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E9%2580%2594%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E6%259C%25B1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%25B7%25AF%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC-%25E7%258D%2584%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%2581%2596%25E8%25AA%2595-12%25E6%259C%258829%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2588%2591%2F%23&d=4gIMu8Ffel0PGVMTRaSpnG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=f6a722a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25A3%258D%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E9%2580%2594%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E6%259C%25B1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%25B7%25AF%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC-%25E7%258D%2584%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%2581%2596%25E8%25AA%2595-12%25E6%259C%258829%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%2588%2591%2F%23&h=5309bfee\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E6%A3%8D%E8%A5%B2%E9%80%94%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E6%9C%B1%E7%B6%93%E7%B7%AF%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC-%E7%8D%84%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%8E%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95-12%E6%9C%8829%E6%97%A5%E5%88%A4%E5%88%91/#</a>"}]}